profile:
Brian's Remote Computer Repair offers remote connection repair for your computer. Just install our remote software then sit back and watch as we tune up and clean up your system. We use a 22 point inspection for your system to make sure it is free of all viruses and malware. We also make sure your system and hardware drivers are up to date and running to their full potential. 

We also make in house calls for home and business. Let us help with your networking setup or repair.

We can also build a custom website and or a custom database for you business.

Please contact us with any concerns or needs for everything computer.
